channel.title: Looking for my source, Rsc-Remix
channel.description:
Ok well when i started rsc-remix, i had no knowledge at anything, and I ended up making some odds and ends in it, like certers, class choosers, and other things, and after I had some decent knowledge I went and upgraded rsc-remix to Rsc-Pkz which had a ton of features, unfortunately I do not have that source anymore, and the dedicated that I had it on expired. So now I'm looking to see if anyone has the rsc-remix source so I can start coding it again, and improve it.
Thanks in advance.
